@prefix coa: <https://example.com/company-ontology-agent#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

coa:Project a owl:Class .
coa:Source a owl:Class .
coa:SourceSpan a owl:Class .
coa:Chunk a owl:Class .
coa:Entity a owl:Class .
coa:Person rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Organization rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Technology rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Concept rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Decision rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Requirement rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Issue rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Task rdfs:subClassOf coa:Entity .
coa:Assertion a owl:Class .
